---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Base title="Back Pikos" description="Support Pikos development. $29 today. When the iPhone app and iCloud sync ship, you get both free.">

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-8 py-20">

    <!-- Back to home -->
    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-gray-400 transition-colors hover:text-orange-500 dark:text-gray-500 dark:hover:text-orange-400">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
      Home
    </a>

    <h1 class="mt-8 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">Back Pikos</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
      $29 today. When the iPhone app and iCloud sync ship, you get both free. No further payment. Until then, you're funding the work.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a
        href="#"
        data-umami-event="backer-purchase"
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg bg-orange-500 px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white transition-colors hover:bg-orange-400"
      >
        Back Pikos · $29
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- The promise -->
    <div class="mt-16 space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">You're buying a promise, not a product</h2>

      <p>
        I'm building Pikos solo, part-time. The desktop app works and you can <a href="/download" class="text-orange-500 hover:underline">use it free today</a>. The iPhone app and sync don't exist yet. They're coming, but I can't promise a date.
      </p>

      <p>
        If I ship, you get the full product at no extra cost. If I don't, you get a refund. No questions.
      </p>

    </div>

    <!-- What backers get -->
    <div class="mt-16 space-y-6 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">What backers get</h2>

      <ul class="ml-1 space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-orange-500" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
          <span class="text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">The Mac App Store version when it ships</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-orange-500" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
          <span class="text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">The iPhone app when it ships</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-orange-500" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
          <span class="text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">iCloud sync across your devices</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-orange-500" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
          <span class="text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">No further payment, ever</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

    </div>

    <!-- FAQ-style sections -->
    <div class="mt-16 space-y-8 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">What if you don't ship?</h2>
        <p class="mt-1">
          Full refund. If plans change, if I drop iOS or stop working on sync, every backer gets their money back.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">What if it takes longer than expected?</h2>
        <p class="mt-1">
          I'll send an honest update. If things slip significantly, I'll offer refunds then too. The commitment is transparency, not a deadline.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Do backers get exclusive features?</h2>
        <p class="mt-1">
          No. Everyone gets the same app. Backing is support, not access to a different tier. The free desktop app stays free and full-featured.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">How do I get the apps when they ship?</h2>
        <p class="mt-1">
          You'll receive App Store promo codes via email. One for the Mac App Store version, one for the iPhone app. Redeem them and the apps are yours.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </main>

  <Footer current="/backer" />
</Base>

<style>
  :global(body) {
    background-color: #fafaf9;
  }

  :global(html.dark body) {
    background-color: #030712;
  }
</style>
